  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Geometric Balance\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Geometric Balance\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-full h-full bg-slate-50 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 font-sans select-none\\\">\\n  <div class=\\\"mb-6 text-center\\\">\\n    <h1 class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800\\\">Tasting Notes App Architecture</h1>\\n    <p class=\\\"text-slate-500 text-sm italic\\\">Jetpack Compose Visual Design Guide</p>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 w-full max-w-[960px] h-[580px]\\\">\\n    <!-- SCREEN 1: HOME (LIST) -->\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] border-[6px] border-slate-900 shadow-xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"h-6 w-1/3 bg-slate-900 mx-auto rounded-b-2xl mb-2\\\"></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"px-5 pt-4 pb-2 flex justify-between items-end\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Collection</p>\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-800\\\">My Cellar</h2>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-amber-100 p-2 rounded-full\\\">\\n          <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-amber-600\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\\\"/></svg>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-hidden px-4 space-y-3 pt-4\\\">\\n        <!-- List Item 1 -->\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-amber-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-amber-800 font-bold\\\">H</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\\\">Hibiki Harmony</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Whisky \342\200\242 2023.10.12</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-amber-500 font-bold\\\">4.5</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <!-- List Item 2 -->\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-rose-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-rose-800 font-bold\\\">C</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\\\">Ch\303\242teau Margaux</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Wine \342\200\242 2023.09.28</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-amber-500 font-bold\\\">5.0</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <!-- List Item 3 -->\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 opacity-60\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-slate-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-slate-800 font-bold\\\">M</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\\\">Macallan 12Y</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Whisky \342\200\242 2023.09.15</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-amber-500 font-bold\\\">4.2</div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"p-4\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-900 text-white py-3 rounded-2xl font-bold text-sm shadow-lg shadow-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">+</span> Add Record\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- SCREEN 2: WRITE (FORM) -->\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] border-[6px] border-slate-900 shadow-xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"h-6 w-1/3 bg-slate-900 mx-auto rounded-b-2xl mb-2\\\"></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-slate-400\\\"><svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\\\"/></svg></div>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-800\\\">New Record</h2>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 px-6 space-y-5 pt-2\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Spirit Name</label>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">The Balvenie 14Y</div>\\n        </div>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Category</label>\\n            <div class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">Whisky</div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div>\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Date</label>\\n            <div class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm text-slate-700 italic\\\">2023.11.05</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div>\\n          <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Rating</label>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center gap-2 px-1\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-amber-500 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-amber-500 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-amber-500 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-200 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-200 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div>\\n          <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Notes</label>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-full h-24 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-3 text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\\\">\\n            Caramel, vanilla, and a hint of spice. Very smooth finish...\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"p-6\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"w-full bg-amber-500 text-white py-3 rounded-2xl font-bold text-sm shadow-lg shadow-amber-100\\\">\\n          Save Experience\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- SCREEN 3: DETAIL -->\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] border-[6px] border-slate-900 shadow-xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"relative h-44 bg-slate-900\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent\\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-4 left-6\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-amber-500 text-[10px] text-white font-bold rounded-lg mb-1 inline-block\\\">Whisky</span>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-white font-bold text-xl\\\">Hibiki Harmony</h3>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute top-4 right-6 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-md rounded-full p-2\\\">\\n          <svg class=\\\"w-4 h-4 text-white\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z\\\"/></svg>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 px-6 pt-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-around mb-6\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase\\\">Nose</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-800 font-bold\\\">Floral</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-[1px] h-8 bg-slate-100\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase\\\">Palate</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-800 font-bold\\\">Honey</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-[1px] h-8 bg-slate-100\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase\\\">Finish</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-800 font-bold\\\">Oak</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-4\\\">\\n          <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"w-1 h-4 bg-amber-500 rounded-full\\\"></span> Personal Note\\n          </h4>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed italic\\\">\\n            \\\"A masterful blend of malt and grain whiskies. The nose is incredibly complex with rose and lychee. The palate is sweet and honey-like with hints of orange peel. A must-have for any collection.\\\"\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-8\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Taste Profile</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[9px] w-12 text-slate-400\\\">Peat</span>\\n              <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-100 overflow-hidden rounded-full\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"w-1/4 h-full bg-amber-400\\\"></div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[9px] w-12 text-slate-400\\\">Sweet</span>\\n              <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-100 overflow-hidden rounded-full\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"w-4/5 h-full bg-amber-400\\\"></div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"p-6 flex gap-3\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-1 border-2 border-slate-100 text-slate-400 py-3 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xs\\\">Edit</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-[2] bg-slate-900 text-white py-3 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xs\\\">Back to List</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"mt-8 flex gap-4 text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\\\">\\n    <span>01. Home</span>\\n    <span class=\\\"text-slate-300\\\">\342\206\222</span>\\n    <span>02. Record Form</span>\\n    <span class=\\\"text-slate-300\\\">\342\206\222</span>\\n    <span>03. Detail View</span>\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Geometric Balance\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Geometric Balance\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-full h-full bg-slate-50 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 font-sans select-none\\\">\\n  <div class=\\\"mb-6 text-center\\\">\\n    <h1 class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800\\\">Tasting Notes App Architecture</h1>\\n    <p class=\\\"text-slate-500 text-sm italic\\\">Jetpack Compose Visual Design Guide</p>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 w-full max-w-[960px] h-[580px]\\\">\\n    <!-- SCREEN 1: HOME (LIST) -->\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] border-[6px] border-slate-900 shadow-xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"h-6 w-1/3 bg-slate-900 mx-auto rounded-b-2xl mb-2\\\"></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"px-5 pt-4 pb-2 flex justify-between items-end\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Collection</p>\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-800\\\">My Cellar</h2>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-amber-100 p-2 rounded-full\\\">\\n          <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-amber-600\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\\\"/></svg>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-hidden px-4 space-y-3 pt-4\\\">\\n        <!-- List Item 1 -->\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-amber-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-amber-800 font-bold\\\">H</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\\\">Hibiki Harmony</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Whisky \342\200\242 2023.10.12</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-amber-500 font-bold\\\">4.5</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <!-- List Item 2 -->\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-rose-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-rose-800 font-bold\\\">C</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\\\">Ch\303\242teau Margaux</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Wine \342\200\242 2023.09.28</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-amber-500 font-bold\\\">5.0</div>\\n        </div>\\n        <!-- List Item 3 -->\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 opacity-60\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-slate-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-slate-800 font-bold\\\">M</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\\\">Macallan 12Y</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Whisky \342\200\242 2023.09.15</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-amber-500 font-bold\\\">4.2</div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"p-4\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-900 text-white py-3 rounded-2xl font-bold text-sm shadow-lg shadow-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">+</span> Add Record\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- SCREEN 2: WRITE (FORM) -->\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] border-[6px] border-slate-900 shadow-xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"h-6 w-1/3 bg-slate-900 mx-auto rounded-b-2xl mb-2\\\"></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-slate-400\\\"><svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\\\"/></svg></div>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-800\\\">New Record</h2>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 px-6 space-y-5 pt-2\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Spirit Name</label>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">The Balvenie 14Y</div>\\n        </div>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Category</label>\\n            <div class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">Whisky</div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div>\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Date</label>\\n            <div class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm text-slate-700 italic\\\">2023.11.05</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div>\\n          <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Rating</label>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center gap-2 px-1\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-amber-500 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-amber-500 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-amber-500 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-200 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-200 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div>\\n          <label class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 block\\\">Notes</label>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-full h-24 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-3 text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\\\">\\n            Caramel, vanilla, and a hint of spice. Very smooth finish...\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"p-6\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"w-full bg-amber-500 text-white py-3 rounded-2xl font-bold text-sm shadow-lg shadow-amber-100\\\">\\n          Save Experience\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- SCREEN 3: DETAIL -->\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] border-[6px] border-slate-900 shadow-xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"relative h-44 bg-slate-900\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent\\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-4 left-6\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-amber-500 text-[10px] text-white font-bold rounded-lg mb-1 inline-block\\\">Whisky</span>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-white font-bold text-xl\\\">Hibiki Harmony</h3>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute top-4 right-6 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-md rounded-full p-2\\\">\\n          <svg class=\\\"w-4 h-4 text-white\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z\\\"/></svg>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 px-6 pt-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-around mb-6\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase\\\">Nose</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-800 font-bold\\\">Floral</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-[1px] h-8 bg-slate-100\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase\\\">Palate</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-800 font-bold\\\">Honey</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-[1px] h-8 bg-slate-100\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase\\\">Finish</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-800 font-bold\\\">Oak</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-4\\\">\\n          <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"w-1 h-4 bg-amber-500 rounded-full\\\"></span> Personal Note\\n          </h4>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed italic\\\">\\n            \\\"A masterful blend of malt and grain whiskies. The nose is incredibly complex with rose and lychee. The palate is sweet and honey-like with hints of orange peel. A must-have for any collection.\\\"\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-8\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Taste Profile</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[9px] w-12 text-slate-400\\\">Peat</span>\\n              <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-100 overflow-hidden rounded-full\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"w-1/4 h-full bg-amber-400\\\"></div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[9px] w-12 text-slate-400\\\">Sweet</span>\\n              <div class=\\\"h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-100 overflow-hidden rounded-full\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"w-4/5 h-full bg-amber-400\\\"></div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"p-6 flex gap-3\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-1 border-2 border-slate-100 text-slate-400 py-3 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xs\\\">Edit</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-[2] bg-slate-900 text-white py-3 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xs\\\">Back to List</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"mt-8 flex gap-4 text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\\\">\\n    <span>01. Home</span>\\n    <span class=\\\"text-slate-300\\\">\342\206\222</span>\\n    <span>02. Record Form</span>\\n    <span class=\\\"text-slate-300\\\">\342\206\222</span>\\n    <span>03. Detail View</span>\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
