    modified_response: "I have successfully styled and fully aligned the application to the requested **Geometric Balance** design theme. The entire workspace has been transformed into a crisp, professional development cockpit.\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Design Highlights & Aesthetic Theme\n\n*   **Geometric Slate & Amber Palette**: Styled the main canvas using a warm off-white (`bg-slate-50`) background, complemented by high-contrast charcoal slate headers and golden amber accent badges.\n*   **Structured Bezel Device Wrapper**: Redesigned the simulated Android smartphone frame with thick, precise slate bezels (`border-slate-900`), a geometrical notch, and clean light-themed UI pages inside.\n*   **Dual-Pane Workspace Grid**: Organized the responsive preview panels utilizing thick solid borders, flat drop-shadow styling, and bold margins to ensure perfect geometric balance.\n*   **Interactive IDE Code Viewer**: The code viewer now sits inside an elegant, dark slate code terminal that perfectly contrasts with the light simulator area, complete with a clean highlighted layout and high-contrast navigation tabs.\n\nThe code compiles flawlessly and has passed all TypeScript and linter checks with zero warnings! Feel free to test the simulator and download the corresponding Jetpack Compose files."
