  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Creating Agent Guidelines**\n\nI\'ve determined that `AGENTS.md` doesn\'t exist at the root level. I\'ll create this file at `/AGENTS.md`. I\'m now focusing on defining the contents of the `AGENTS.md` file. It will contain clear, customized behavior rules to guide the AI agent during its coding tasks.\n\n\n**Defining Project Parameters**\n\nI\'m now outlining the critical parameters for the project within the `AGENTS.md` file. I\'ve begun by clarifying the project\'s core purpose. The intent is to generate Kotlin code using Jetpack Compose that mirrors the UI/UX simulated within a React-based virtual simulator for a Jetpack Compose liquor tasting journal app. Furthermore, I\'m setting a core goal: ensuring the simulator and generated Kotlin code always stay synchronized. Finally, the design should adhere to a \"Honey & Oak\" theme with bold, geometric borders, evoking a clean, Neo-Brutalism aesthetic.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 11
      nanos: 793905179
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
